    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Planned works, such as works of art or architecture, that were never physically produced. For architecture more specifically, use "unbuilt projects."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
